sentences: During the morning spin-off group on numbers/text, parties focused on drafting clear options for inclusion in the AWG-KP Chair s revised text that will be forwarded to ministers for consideration.
Parties considered text on Protocol amendments, eligibility to participate in the flexibility mechanisms, carry-over of surplus AAUs, and the share of proceeds.
Parties had before them new proposals on some of these issues, as well as text consolidating previous proposals.
Parties agreed on which proposals should be forwarded to the AWG-KP Chair for inclusion in her revised text, and the spin-off group concluded its work.
